        The network layer is similar to the transport layer. Recall that the transport layer allows applications to communicate. 
        The network layer allows <em>hosts</em> (or computers/phones/etc.) to communicate. 
        The protocol in this layer that we're most interested in is the Internet Protocol (IP).
    </p>

